title.rendered: What Languages is Dumpster Available In?

content.rendered:
Dumpster is currently available in the following languages:

  • English
  • German
  • Spanish
  • French
  • Portuguese
  • Hindi
  • Russian
  • Japanese
  • Chinese Simplified
  • Korean
  • Turkish
  • Hebrew
  • Arabic
  • Italian
  • Indonesian 
  • Vietnamese

We’re always working on adding & supporting more languages, so stay tuned if you don’t see your preferred language listed!
